alex.mojaki.boxes.middleware.symmetric

Class SymmetricMiddleware<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • alex.mojaki.boxes.middleware.symmetric.SymmetricMiddleware<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChangeMiddleware<T>, GetMiddleware<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultValue, EnsureBounds

    public abstract class SymmetricMiddleware<T>
extends Object
implements ChangeMiddleware<T>, GetMiddleware<T>
    Middleware which implements both GetMiddleware and ChangeMiddleware with the same effect on values.

        Call apply(PowerBox, Object, Object) with the same parameters.
        Specified by:
        onGet in interface GetMiddleware<T>
        Parameters:
        box - the PowerBox whose value is being obtained by get.
        originalValue - the value the box contained before any middleware was applied.
        currentValue - for the first middleware in the sequence, this is the same as originalValue. For subsequent middleware, this is the return value of the previous middleware.
